arrows.description: Ambition is a shaft that over the years has enjoyed considerable success and a wide audience of admirers in various fields of use from target shooting to 3D. The shaft comes complete with nock, pin and uninstalled tip, to be cut to the required size and then glued. The wide availability of pins and components, typical of top level arrows, make it the ideal shaft for first competitions and for those looking for an excellent product at an unbeatable price.

Carbon shaft with an inner diameter of 4.2mm in a bamboo look. Very beautiful and elegant, supplied with nock collar and with straightness of +/- 0.003". Robust shaft with a traditional look for the 3D field.

Sturdy and fast 32" carbon shaft with camo design (straightness 0.003 "), dedicated to hunting. Available with spine of 400 and 500 with internal diameter of 6.2 mm. Excellent value, available as a shaft or arrow.

Good quality carbon shaft recommended for universal use. Available both as an unfletched shaft and as a fletched arrow with plastic or natural vanes. Despite its low weight, which allows it to achieve a very good velocity, its a very sturdy shaft. Available with spine from 400 to 800, with an internal diameter of 6.2 mm and straightness of ± 0.006". Its features allow it to be used with either traditional hunting bows, bare bows or compound bows.
Shaft made of high-quality carbon available with spine from 250 to 1000 with an internal diameter of 4.2 mm, precise and robust shaft suitable for target and 3D shooting. Pin already inserted.

The Cross-X Plurima shaft is made of a high module carbon (40 tons), precise (straightness +/- 0.001") and available in spines from 350 to 800 (10 different sizes) with internal diameter of 3.2 mm.The Cross-X Plurima is a strong and precise shaft to obtain maximum performance in target shooting,suitable for both compound and olympic archers.Inside components compatible with the one of the X10

The new carbon Ambition shaft is characterized by new graphics and above all is a selected shaft (straightness is now +/- 0.003 ") to offer greater performance. The shaft is complete with nock and pin, and the tip is not installed and is designed to be cut to the necessary size and then glued. The wide availability of plugs and the internal components, proper of high level arrows make it the ideal auction for the first competitions and for those looking for an excellent product at an unbeatable price. In this particular version, this version comes with a silver colored crest, which makes it even more appealing.

The Madera is a product born for the traditional market. Reliable and robust, its the ideal choice for all those looking for a valid alternative to wooden arrows. The Madera is available as shaft with straightness +/-0.006" and as a complete arrow in a more affordable version with straightness +/-0.010".

For everyone who is looking for an excellent product at a more competitive price, Cross-X offers the Cube version of the Plurima shaft. The Plurima Cube has the same weight and spine characteristic but with straightness of +-/- 0.003". The shaft is sold in a 12 pieces pack with installed pin. Each dozen is selected and grouped by weight and spine.

Based on Plurima shaft, Cross-X offers Exentia: a product suitable for those with a more limited budget that still wants to be able to use a shaft of the highest level. The weight characteristics remain the same but in this case the straightness is +/- 0.005 ". Only available as shaft with pins for the installation of all the nock pin available on the market.

Large diameter shaft, designed for indoor archery. Its straightness (±0.001") and weight consistency guarantee maximum precision. Bare shaft without components, to be completed with point and pin adapter or bushing.

An extremely versatile shaft that, thanks to the use of a 40-ton high module carbon, offers an incredible lightness that makes it suitable for many uses, from target shooting to field shooting and also 3D. Pins included.

The Hurricane is an extremely versatile shaft, utilizing 40-ton high-modulus carbon to offer incredible lightness, making it suitable for multiple uses from target shooting to field and even 3D archery. All shafts come with insert nock 4,2 included.

Shaft made of high quality carbon available in spines from 350 to 1000 with an internal diameter of 4.2 mm. Precise and robust suitable for target shooting, field and 3D. Dedicated internal components. The Maior shaft is avaiable in three differente levels of straightness.

Shaft made of high quality carbon available in spines from 350 to 1000 with an internal diameter of 4.2 mm. Precise and robust suitable for target shooting, field and 3D. Dedicated internal components. The Maior shaft is avaiable in three differente levels of straightness: MAIOR CUBE - straightness ± 0.003", MAIOR PENTA - straightness ± 0.005", MAIOR OCTAGON - straightness ± 0.008"

The Ambition shaft that has proven over the years its own quality, now presents itself in the new Gold Edition version that, in addition to the golden finish on the back of the shaft, presents a remarkable straightness of +/- 0.001" proposing itself as a great choice for target shooting. Pin and pin nock included. Points not included!

Extremely lightweight and sturdy carbon shaft with 6.2 mm inside diameter. Available in 400 to 800 spine. Shaft ideal for target and 3D archery. Sold complete with 6.2 nocks (already installed) and inserts (not installed). Straightness: ± 0.002"

The Madera Light offers great speed thanks to its low weight and is therefore particularly suitable for 3D competitions or for all those looking for a fast and performing arrow. The Madera Light is available as a shaft with +/-0.003" straightness or as a +/- 0.010" straightness arrow. The shaft comes with inserted nock and loose insert.

Light, Fast and yet stable carbon shaft. Ideal for 3D shooting thanks to the 5.2mm internal diameter. The Penta version with a straightness of ±0.005" is the entry level of the Avatar family. The ideal shaft for all those looking for a thin shaft without going to OD 4.2mm. The Avatar is also appreciated for its excellent flight characteristics and a very flat trajectory. A quality shaft at a competitive price.

Version of the Avatar CUBE with cresting, very beautiful and elegant. Light, Fast and yet stable carbon shaft. Ideal for 3D shooting thanks to the 5.2mm internal diameter. The Cube version with 0.003" straightness is the best of the Avatar family. The ideal shaft for all those looking for a thin shaft without going to OD 4.2mm. The Avatar is also appreciated for its excellent flight characteristics and a very flat trajectory. A quality shaft at a competitive price.

Large diameter shaft, designed for indoor archery. Its straightness (+/- 0.008") and weight consistency guarantee good precision at an affordable price. Bare shaft without components, to be completed with point and pin adapter or bushing.

Light, Fast and yet stable carbon shaft. Ideal for 3D shooting thanks to the 5.2mm internal diameter. The Cube version with 0.003" straightness is the best of the Avatar family. The ideal shaft for all those looking for a thin shaft without going to OD 4.2mm. The Avatar is also appreciated for its excellent flight characteristics and a very flat trajectory. A quality shaft at a competitive price.
A very versatile shaft, suitable for target and 3D range. The Pegasus is light and very robust and available in 3 gradations of straightness. Shaft with straightness +/- 0.003". Complete with pin.

High-quality carbon shaft with an inner diameter of 4.2 mm. Due to the inner diameter, it is a small diameter shaft for which a variety of compatible components are available on the market. The weight is low so that the arrow can reach higher speeds and has a tight parabola. The Pegasus is recommended for target shooting, especially 3D shooting, thanks to its lightness, precision and robustness.
Lightweight and strong carbon rod with an internal diameter of 6.2mm. Available in spine from 400 to 800. Shaft suitable for target and 3D shooting.

Extremely versatile shaft suitable for multiple uses from Target to 3D shooting. Light and strong, the CUBE version has straightness 0.003" and with decorated cresting in the rear part of the shaft, giving the shaft a better look by improving also the visibility on the target.

3K carbon shaft which guarantees superior strength and an incomparable carbon look. Available as shaft or complete arrow. Straightness +/- 0.006". The shaft is complete with 6.2 nock and unglued insert.

A very robust shaft with a 5.2mm internal diameter and a straightness of 0.006" oriented for approach shooting or 3D courses. Total shaft length for all sizes is 31". Shaft complete with inserted 5.2 nock.
Inexpensive shaft with internal diameter of 6,2 mm and straightness of ±0.010, ideal for both compound and traditional bows. Includes nocks (inserted) and inserts (not inserted).

The Cross-X Iridium shaft has the same construction as the Cross-X Element shaft (full carbon), but thanks to the bright colours of the crest it is immediately recognisable. The Iridium shaft is supplied with a 4,2 mm insert nock. Straightness : ± 0.006"

The Fulmen XXL shaft has a dual purpose, suitable for both Indoor and 3D shooting. This shaft is characterized by an internal diameter of 8.0 mm and a generous outer diameter of about 9 mm (variable depending on spines), making it suitable for capturing some line points, but above all, it is an extremely lightweight shaft that is particularly suitable for 3D shooting at unknown distances. Straightness +/- 0.002". Available in a range of spines from 250 to 500 and comes with a 6.2 mm nock bushing.

Light, Fast and yet stable carbon shaft. Ideal for 3D shooting thanks to the 5.2mm internal diameter. The Penta version with a straightness of ±0.008" is the entry level of the Avatar family. The ideal shaft for all those looking for a thin shaft without going to OD 4.2mm. The Avatar is also appreciated for its excellent flight characteristics and a very flat trajectory. A quality shaft at a competitive price.

The Fulmen XXL Penta shaft has a dual purpose, on the one hand indoor shooting and on the other hand 3D shooting. This shaft is distinguished by an inner diameter of 8.0 mm and a generous outer diameter of approx. 9 mm (which varies depending on the spines), making it suitable for gaining a few line points, but above all it is an extremely light shaft which makes it particularly suitable for 3D shooting at unknown distances. Straightness +/- 0.005’.

Asta in carbonio di alta qualità, di diametro interno 4.2 mm. Il diametro interno la classifica come asta di diametro sottile, e per questa misura sono disponibili sul mercato numerosissimi componenti compatibili. Il peso è contenuto e permette quindi alla freccia di raggiungere maggiori velocità e di avere una parabola tesa. La Pegasus è consigliata per il tiro targa, e soprattutto per il tiro 3D, grazie alla sua leggerezza, precisione e robustezza. Rettilineità ±0.003".

Unique on the market for its characteristics, the new Fulmen XL is the right choice for 3D compound shooters, for all categories of barebow archery and for compound bows with limited draw lengths and poundage. A shaft with an internal diameter of 7.6 that can be used with either glue-in or screw-in points (not included), super unibushing already installed.
